    "plot_shap("income")",
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bf9df879",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Unlike the zip code score plot, income does not act as a strong proxy, so the group patterns overlap more."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c48271ca",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### If, instead, you were the **reviewer**, what other questions might you ask the person who built this model? Give at least two."
   ]
  },
